TL;DR SUMMARY (UNOFFICIAL):
This Covenant grants free, perpetual use of the Work to individuals and hobbyists, but requires commercial entities with over $100,000 USD in annual revenue to purchase a commercial license after a 40-day evaluation period. Machine learning models and artificial intelligence systems are strictly prohibited from training on this Work without a separate training license. Violation of these terms triggers reasonable liquidated damages, willful damage multipliers, and public disclosure of infringement. The Work is provided "as is" with standard liability disclaimers.

